_Department\" title=\"UC Santa Barbara Physics Department\" class=\"mw-redirect\">UC Santa Barbara Physics Department<\/a> and is currently affiliated with the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http:\/\/www.quantum.chapman.edu\">Institute for Quantum Studies<\/a> at Chapman University in California.<\/p>","name":"David J. Gross","place_of_birth":"Washington, D.C.","place_of_death":null,"text":"David J. Gross , Physics, 2004","year":2004.0}